\id PHM
\h Filemon
\toc1 Filemon
\toc2 Filemon
\toc3 Filemon
\mt1 FILEMON
\c 1
\p 
\v 1 O Filemon, e Pol. E Kristus Yesus aqa wau tamo. E aqa anjam mare mare laqnem deqa jeu tamo naŋgi na e ojsib tonto talq endi waibeb unum. Aqo gago was Timoti wo anjam endi neŋgreŋyosim inoq qariŋyonum. Ni gago Kristen was bole. Ni iga koba na wau qujai.
\v 2 Aqo aiyel anjam endi ni qa ti gago jaja Apia qa ti Arkipus qa ti Kristen tamo uŋgasari kalil ino talq di loueqnub qaji naŋgi qa ti qariŋyonum. Arkipus a iga koba na qoto tamo bulosim Qotei aqa wau ojeqnum.
\p 
\v 3 Gago Abu Qotei wo Tamo Koba Yesus Kristus wo naŋgi aiyel niŋgi qa are boleinjrimqa niŋgi lawo na soqniy.
\s1 Filemon a kumbra tulaŋ boledamu yoqnej deqa Pol a areboleboleiyoqnej
\p 
\v 4 E gaigai ijo Qotei biŋiyoqnsim ni qa pailyeqnum.
\v 5 E ni qa anjam endegsi queqnum, ni na Tamo Koba Yesus tulaŋ qalaqalaiyoqnsim a qa ino areqalo siŋgilateqnum. Osim ni na Qotei aqa segi tamo uŋgasari kalil naŋgi dego qalaqalainjreqnum.
\v 6 Ni iga ti beterosim koba na Yesus qa gago areqalo siŋgilateqnum deqa e endegsi Qotei pailyeqnum, “O Abu, ni na Filemon iga ti aqaryaigimqa iga powo bole osim iŋgi bole bole Kristus a iga egeqnu qaji di geregere poigwas.”
\v 7 Od, was, e qalieonum, ni na Qotei aqa segi tamo uŋgasari kalil naŋgi qalaqalainjroqnsim naŋgo are tulaŋ siŋgilatetnjreqnum. Ino kumbra dena ijo are latetbeqnaqa e areboleboleibeqnu.
\s1 Pol na Filemon minjej, “Ni na Onesimus qalaqalaiyime”
\p 
\v 8 O Filemon, e qalieonum, ino kumbra kalil bole. Deqa e ni kumbra bei yqajqa mermitqa ni ijo anjam daurye. E Kristus aqa ñam na ni siŋgila na mermqa kere.
\v 9 Ariya e ni tulaŋ siŋgila na mermqasai. Aqo ombla qalaqalaiyo kumbra dauryeqnum deqa e ni lawo na mermqai. E Pol. E Kristus Yesus aqa wau tamo. E aqa anjam mare mare laqnem deqa jeu tamo naŋgi na e ojsib tonto talq endi waibeb unum.
\v 10 E tonto talq endi sonamqa ino kaŋgal tamo Onesimus a ni uratmosiq ulaŋosiq Rom qure endeq bosiq e itbej. E itbonaqa e Yesus aqa anjam minjnamqa a are bulyosiq Yesus qa aqa areqalo siŋgilatej. Deqa bini a ijo aŋgro bul unu. Deqa e ni mermqai, ni a kumbra bole osoryime.
\v 11 A nami kaŋgal tamo bolesai soqnej deqa a ni qa wau bole yosaioqnej. Ariya bini a kaŋgal tamo bolequja unu deqa a ni qa wau bole yoqnqa kere. A e qa dego wau bole yoqnqa kere.
\p 
\v 12 Ariya endego e Onesimus qariŋyonum a inoq olo bqo. Deqa e a qa are ugeibqo. Di kiyaqa? E a tulaŋ qalaqalaiyeqnum deqa.
\v 13 E Yesus aqa anjam bole qa waueqnum deqa e tonto talq endi unum. Ariya ijo are koba endegsi unu. E Onesimus olo osiy a e ombla tonto talq endi sosim a na e aqaryaiboqnqas. A ino kaŋgal tamo unu deqa a na e aqaryaibqas di ni na dego e aqaryaibqam.
\v 14 Ariya e Onesimus qariŋyonum inoq olo bqo. E endegsi are qalonum. Ni na e aqaryaibqa are soqnim ni ino segi areqalo na e odbosim Onesimus olo ijoq qariŋye. E siŋgila na ni mermqasai.
\p 
\v 15 Bole, Onesimus a bati truquyala ni uratmej. E are qalonum, Qotei a segi na gam gereiyonaqa Onesimus a ni uratmej. Di kiyaqa? Ni na a olo osim niŋgi ombla bati gaigai sqajqa deqa.
\v 16 Onesimus a ino kaŋgal tamo segi sai. A ino Kristen was bole. A ijo Kristen was dego. Deqa e a tulaŋ qalaqalaiyeqnum. A ino kaŋgal tamo bolequja. A ni ombla Tamo Koba beteryejunub. Deqa e qalieonum, ni a olo tulaŋ qalaqalaiyoqnqam.
\p 
\v 17 Ni e ombla Yesus aqa wau tamo unum edegosim Onesimus osim geregereiyoqne. Ni e osim geregereibeqnum dego kere.
\v 18 Onesimus a une bei ni emej kiyo? A ino silali bei nami yaimosiq olo ni emqajqa mermosiqa bunuqna ni emosai kiyo? Degamqa ni na merbimqa e kamba silali di keretosiy ni olo emqai.
\v 19 E Pol. Anjam endi e ijo segi baŋ na neŋgreŋyonum. Ni e merbimqa Onesimus a ino silali bei yaimej qaji di e na kamba olo ni emekritqai. Ariya ni que. Nami e Yesus aqa anjam ni mermonam qusim are bulyem. E ino qunuŋ qa aqaryaimem. Deqa e ni endegsi mermqa kere, ni na kamba olo ino segi ŋambile e ebekritime. Ariya e degsi ni mermqa uratonum.
\v 20 O ijo was Filemon, ni que. Aqo ombla Tamo Koba Kristus aqa tamo unum deqa ni aqa ñam na olo Onesimus ijoq qariŋyosim dena ijo are boletetbe.
\p 
\v 21 E qalieonum, ni ijo anjam endi dauryqam. Osim ijo anjam endi buŋyosim olo Onesimus ijoq qariŋyqam. Utru deqa e anjam endi neŋgreŋyonum.
\v 22 Ijo anjam qujai bei agiende. E are qalonum, Qotei a nuŋgo pailyo qusim gam waqtetbimqa e nuŋgoq olo bqai. Deqa Filemon, e ino talq di ŋeiqajqa warum bei ni na gereiyetbe.
\s1 Pol aqa wau qujai naŋgi na Filemon kaiyeiyeb
\p 
\v 23 Aqo Epafras wo ombla tonto talq endi unum. Epafras a dego Kristus Yesus aqa wau tamo. A Yesus aqa anjam mare mare laqnej deqa jeu tamo naŋgi na a ojsib tonto talq endi waiyeb unu. A na ni kaiyeimqo.
\v 24 Mak na Aristarkus na Demas na Luk na naŋgi qolqe dego ni kaiyeimonub. Naŋgi e koba na wau qujai.
\p 
\v 25 Tamo Koba Yesus Kristus a niŋgi qa are boleiyosim nuŋgo qunuŋ geregere taqatoqneme. Bole. 
